            <th scope="row"><b>Description: </b></th>
            <td style="padding-left: 4px;"><div><p>IMMZ.D18.S.DTP.On-time start schedule
Diphtheria–tetanus–pertussis (DTP) vaccination schedule, on-time start (at ≤ 12 months of age)</p>
</div></td>
        </tr>
        

        
